    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37516</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ね？　さっき変な声しなかった？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey? Didn’t you hear a strange voice earlier?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <StructId>1</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37816</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>変な声？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A strange voice?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <StructId>2</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38008</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルール</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kruel</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <StructId>3</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>14</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38356</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>悲鳴みたいな、ちょっと変な声</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It sounded like a scream, kind of strange.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <StructId>4</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38808</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;MEL&gt;って耳いいよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;MEL&gt;, you’ve got good ears, huh?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <StructId>5</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39080</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その声は、奥へと立ち入ろうとして魔物に
食い殺された数々の恨みを抱いた霊の数々の声……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That voice... it’s the cries of countless spirits, filled with resentment, devoured by monsters as they tried to venture deeper...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <StructId>6</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>16</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41544</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……ってあれ？　怖くないのか、&lt;MEL&gt;？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Wait, &lt;MEL&gt;, aren’t you scared?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <StructId>7</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>16</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42068</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>幽霊とかウソですよね？
だってここ変な感じとかしないですし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ghosts aren’t real, right? I mean, this place doesn’t feel weird or anything.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <StructId>8</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42892</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>へ、変な感じ……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-weird feeling...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <StructId>9</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そうでも、そういう時はきゃあとか
怖がった方が可愛いぜ？　な？　&lt;DIO&gt;</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even so, it’s cuter to scream or act scared in moments like this, right? Isn’t that right, &lt;DIO&gt;?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <StructId>10</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>16</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44180</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　あ、ああ、うん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Oh, yeah, sure...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <StructId>11</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;MEL&gt;は脅かしがいがないな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;MEL&gt;, you’re no fun to scare.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <StructId>12</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>16</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46196</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_002_044_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　あ、ちょ、ちょっと、みんなどこ行ったんだ！
ひ、ひとりにすんなよ、え？　あ、おい……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? W-wait, where did everyone go?! D-don’t leave me alone! Hey? H-hey...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <StructId>13</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
